{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[A]Forward troubles Illinois, lock the front door, [F#m]oh boy
[D]Look at all the happy creatures [A]dancing on the [E]lawn
[A]Bother me tomorrow, [F#m]today I'll find no sorrow
